Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:04.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}知らず誰かに甘え
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:06.29,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}人を傷付け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:08.69,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逃げ場所作ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:10.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}だけど今日これからは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:12.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}止まってられない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:14.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}明日に猛ダッシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:17.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}スピード上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:20.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}時代を超えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:24.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}素敵な未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:26.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}きっと待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:29.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}希望の声が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.91,0:23:32.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}聴こえてくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:36.30,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ゴールは近い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:39.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あと少し走ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:20.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\an9}用自由的顏色畫畫看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:27.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\an9}一定能看到  新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:41.36,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}一生一次的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不會錯過的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:47.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}絕對不會偷工減料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:50.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}一定要把它完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:53.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}要是害怕失敗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:56.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}想要都要不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}總比後悔好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:01.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}來進攻吧！
